Package: ForesToolboxRS
Type: Package
Title: Remote Sensing Tools for Forest Monitoring
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Yonatan Tarazona
Maintainer: Yonatan Tarazona <geoyons@gmail.com>
Description: Remote sensing tools for forest monitoring includes a series of 
    novel techniques to detect disturbances in the forest through optical images 
    and fusion of optical and microwave data. All tools are based on scientific 
    publications.
